His name was Jojo, though I never saw him; I only heard stories about him and people saying be on the look out.  For me, the scariest thing in Innothule was the original Spore Guardian.  Anyone remember how he used to have a nasty proc that spun you around forever?  It made it virtually impossible for you to escape him.  By the time you stopped spinning, you'd either be turned around and running back into him, or only make it a few steps away only to get hit with the proc again.  <br>
